data.description: Welcome Home.... Quiet Country Setting -Oversized double corner lot located in West Highlands. NO HOA. Featuring this three bedroom, two bath split floor plan home with Family room plus Living room for additional gathering space. Oversized walk-in kitchen with pantry for food storage, loads of counter space and cabinets. Rear family room also provides access to the enclosed office or 4th bedroom (no closet) for growing families or spare room for overnight family visits. New exterior French doors also allow for come and go access to the rear office area. New Roof and Gutters system in 2021. The HVAC unit was also replaced in 2018. Home also features a full two car oversized garage with side door access. Exterior bonuses... two metal storage sheds, over a half-acre of land, and an inground swimming pool with updated screen enclosure (2018) . Privacy fenced yard along the east lot line with a wooded buffer to the west proving the perfect sunset over the treetops at dusk.  Pool Parties all summer long in the detached screened inground pool area with tiki bar and lounging furniture. Huge private playground with swing set and fort platform area with cargo net entrance for the littles. Large Live oaks and mature fruit trees canopy the rear yard throughout. Inquire today.
